> The Cook Unit is redeemable in product or service.



Working Capital Partnership ("Guarantee Society")


that includes workers and consumers issues credit with reference to the Cook Unit, and in return workers and consumers employ capital. 

 an agreement that places assets to be used by the Guarantee Society
 under nominal custody.
 Before this time when agreement is made and a Custodian formed the assets exist in a fragmented state often with misaligned interests...think of this state as 'matter unorganized.' We're going to organize it...align the interests in the same direction. The Custodian enforces an agreement and just kind of 'watches until all obey.' His Steward, the Manager/Service Provider/Bishop's Agent manages the process on a daily basis, making sure to keep title and transaction registries in order. 

The Asset Creators as it were utilize the proceeds of revenue-stream investors to acquire more assets. Farmers and consumers might see fit to expand farming infrastructure by forming an asset chain with the proceeds. Maybe they throw more farmland into the works, warehouses, processing facilities, a refinery, an electrical generation facility etc.
